  
<h1>Welcome to the Super Hero Team Creator</h1>
<h2>Create a Team and Heroes!</h2>

<form action="/teams" method="post">
  <h3>Any Super Hero Team needs a cool name and motto!</h3>
  <p>Team Name: <input id="team[name]" type="text" name="team[name]"/></p>
  <p>Team Motto: <input id="team[motto]" type="text" name="team[motto]"/></p>

  <h3>Any decent Super Hero Team needs at least three members!</h3>
  <h4>Hero 1:</h4>
  <p>Hero Name: <input id="member1_name" type="text" name="team[heroes][][name]"/></p>
  <p>Hero Power: <input id="member1_power" type="text" name="team[heroes][][power]"/></p>
  <p>Hero Biography: <input id="member1_bio" type="text" name="team[heroes][][bio]"/></p>
  <h4>Hero 2:</h4>
  <p>Hero Name: <input id="member2_name" type="text" name="team[heroes][][name]"/></p>
  <p>Hero Power: <input id="member2_power" type="text" name="team[heroes][][power]"/></p>
  <p>Hero Biography: <input id="member2_bio" type="text" name="team[heroes][][bio]"/></p>
  <h4>Hero 3:</h4>
  <p>Hero Name: <input id="member3_name" type="text" name="team[heroes][][name]"/></p>
  <p>Hero Power: <input id="member3_power" type="text" name="team[heroes][][power]"/></p>
  <p>Hero Biography: <input id="member3_bio" type="text" name="team[heroes][][bio]"/></p>
  <input type="submit" name="submit" id="submit">
</form>